Package: pickart
Type: Package
Title: Extract information of artworks in the MET museum by API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Xueying", "Huang", email = "xh2434@columbia.edu",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Xueying Huang <xh2434@columbia.edu>
Description: Extract information of artworks in the MET museum by API in R. 
    It combines several functions that allow users to find artworks by departments, 
    date, classification etc. It also help users to find artworks belonging to 
    certain theme or topic. Users can choose to download the images, maps 
    and related artworks information by functions in this package.
